      "text": "Excellent! I found a lot of files. Let me now read the most important ones to understand what LAMPForge is. I'll read:\n\n1. The README.md (top-level)\n2. RAEng_Technical_Report_Local_AI_Optimization.md\n3. docs/ARCHITECTURE.md\n4. Maybe also some other key files\n\nLet me also look at the source code files to understand the languages used.",
