      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\LAMPForge_SDTP\\forge-flow-learn-0d5b3821\\curriculum\\05-lampforge-sdtp\\_module.forge</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: protocol: forge/1.0\n2: type: module\n3: \n4: metadata:\n5:   id: lampforge-sdtp\n6:   title: \"LAMPForge & SDTP\"\n7:   description: |\n8:     Learn to use and extend the LAMPForge Pedagogical Development Environment\n9:     and the Software-Defined Training Protocol (SDTP).\n10:   duration_minutes: 280\n11:   difficulty: intermediate\n12:   order: 5\n13: \n14: objectives:\n15:   - understand: \"The .forge protocol specification\"\n16:   - apply: \"Write project-level .forge files\"\n17:   - apply: \"Configure runtime environments\"\n18:   - apply: \"Implement FinOps governance\"\n19:   - apply: \"Create curriculum with lesson-level .forge files\"\n20:   - understand: \"Deployment options (browser-native, devcontainer, cloud)\"\n21: \n22: lessons:\n23:   - id: 01-understanding-forge-protocol\n24:     title: \"Understanding the .forge Protocol\"\n25:     duration: 35\n26:   - id: 02-writing-your-first-forge-file\n27:     title: \"Writing Your First .forge File\"\n28:     duration: 30\n29:   - id: 03-runtime-configuration\n30:     title: \"Runtime Configuration\"\n31:     duration: 35\n32:   - id: 04-finops-governance\n33:     title: \"FinOps Governance in .forge\"\n34:     duration: 35\n35:   - id: 05-evidence-collection\n36:     title: \"Evidence Collection for Portfolios\"\n37:     duration: 30\n38:   - id: 06-browser-native-pde\n39:     title: \"Deploying to Browser-Native PDE\"\n40:     duration: 35\n41:   - id: 07-devcontainer-deployment\n42:     title: \"Devcontainer Deployment\"\n43:     duration: 35\n44:   - id: 08-creating-curriculum\n45:     title: \"Creating Curriculum with Lesson-Level .forge\"\n46:     duration: 45\n47: \n48: curriculum:\n49:   frameworks:\n50:     - name: AWS re/Start\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 55. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>",
