e/CLIPanel.tsx` | CLI command panel |\n| `src/components/pde/SQLWorkbenchPanel.tsx` | SQL workbench panel |\n| `src/components/pde/EvidencePanel.tsx` | Evidence timeline panel |\n| `src/components/pde/PanelToggleBar.tsx` | Panel visibility controls |\n| `src/components/pde/RuntimeStatusPanel.tsx` | Runtime status display |\n| `src/components/pde/AIStatus.tsx` | AI inference status |\n| `src/components/pde/InferenceLog.tsx` | AI inference log |\n| `src/components/pde/PolicyManager.tsx` | Policy governance manager |\n| `src/components/pde/SystemDiagnostics.tsx` | System diagnostics |\n| `src/components/pde/IDEConfig.tsx` | IDE configuration component |\n\n**Curriculum (`curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/`):**\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/_module.forge` | Module definition (280 min, 8 lessons) |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/01-understanding-forge-protocol.forge` | SDTP protocol introduction |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/02-writing-your-first-forge-file.forge` | Hands-on .forge file creation |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/03-runtime-configuration.forge` | Runtime environment configuration |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/04-finops-governance.forge` | FinOps governance in .forge |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/05-evidence-collection.forge` | Evidence collection for portfolios |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/06-browser-native-pde.forge` | Browser-native PDE deployment |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/07-devcontainer-deployment.forge` | Devcontainer deployment |\n| `curriculum/05-lampforge-sdtp/08-creating-curriculum.forge` | Creating curriculum with lesson-level .forge |\n\n**Examples (`examples/`):**\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `examples/minimal.forge` | Minimal two-field example |\n| `examples/wjec-unit4.forge` | WJEC A2 Digital Technology Unit 4 |\n| `examples/aws-restart.forge` | AWS re/Start cloud retraining |\n| `examples/code-institute.forge` | Code Institute full-stack